1
00:01:21,430 --> 00:01:26,990
[Brocade Odyssey]

2
00:01:27,210 --> 00:01:29,810
[Episode 17]

3
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,870
Even if the day comes when I must marry,

4
00:01:32,630 --> 00:01:33,870
I would seek

5
00:01:33,870 --> 00:01:35,440
a man who can share with me

6
00:01:35,590 --> 00:01:36,630
the trials and triumphs of life,

7
00:01:37,230 --> 00:01:38,630
one who will stand beside me in battle.

8
00:01:41,510 --> 00:01:42,440
And that person is not you.

9
00:01:45,230 --> 00:01:46,040
I'm sorry.

10
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,120
I don't care at all.

11
00:02:22,670 --> 00:02:23,670
I'm sorry.

12
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,880
I don't want to hurt you,

13
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,880
but I don't want to keep

14
00:02:28,390 --> 00:02:30,190
giving you false hope either.

15
00:02:30,470 --> 00:02:31,720
That would be worse.

16
00:02:34,610 --> 00:02:37,900
[Bai Residence]

17
00:02:42,550 --> 00:02:43,750
Have Zhou Wang

18
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:45,390
replicate all the patterns

19
00:02:45,390 --> 00:02:46,440
he's woven before.

20
00:02:47,030 --> 00:02:48,440
Tell him to buy

21
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:49,600
some looms and silk thread secretly.

22
00:02:49,630 --> 00:02:50,960
And then, ship them in batches to Nanzhao.

23
00:02:51,110 --> 00:02:53,160
Remember, don't leave any traces.

24
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,470
As for that pattern brought back

25
00:02:55,470 --> 00:02:56,960
by the Yu family from Gubei Village,

26
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,000
do you want me to steal it?

27
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,000
Let's leave it with Ji Yingying.

28
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:02,960
I believe she'll surprise me.

29
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:07,240
Didn't you want to use that pattern

30
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,630
to win over the Yu family?

31
00:03:09,550 --> 00:03:10,960
But now, Ji Yingying

32
00:03:11,110 --> 00:03:13,550
is more important to me than the Yu family.

33
00:03:14,390 --> 00:03:15,830
Rather than winning over the Yu family,

34
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:18,600
it's better to win over Ji Yingying.

35
00:03:43,670 --> 00:03:44,520
Yingying,

36
00:03:45,670 --> 00:03:46,960
Mr. Yang is looking for you.

37
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,600
What does he want?

38
00:03:50,830 --> 00:03:52,240
Isn't there enough trouble already?

39
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:53,910
Yaoting,

40
00:03:53,910 --> 00:03:55,320
tell him I'm busy.

41
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,160
Looks like...

42
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,320
you are really busy.

43
00:04:01,670 --> 00:04:02,520
I'll let you guys talk.

44
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,630
Shu Red Silk is being dyed.

45
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,440
You're supervising

46
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:12,520
a bit too frequently.

47
00:04:13,470 --> 00:04:15,160
After all, it's tribute brocade silk.

48
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:17,550
We can never be too careful.

49
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,160
Then, have a look.

50
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:20,230
Is this Shu Red

51
00:04:20,550 --> 00:04:21,950
the same as the one you had in mind?

52
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:13,110
I visited Mr. Yu.

53
00:05:13,510 --> 00:05:14,920
I know what happened in the village.

54
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,160
I've also looked into Bai Sheng.

55
00:05:24,550 --> 00:05:26,200
He's a smart merchant

56
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:27,350
with an unclear background

57
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:28,350
and unclear intentions.

58
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:29,790
I know this.

59
00:05:33,670 --> 00:05:35,230
But in Yizhou,

60
00:05:35,230 --> 00:05:36,600
most merchants

61
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,950
have some hidden depths

62
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:39,040
and aren't really harmless.

63
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:40,640
At least he's not afraid of the Niu family

64
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:41,720
or the Zhao family.

65
00:05:43,230 --> 00:05:44,160
If necessary,

66
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,440
rather than choosing someone tangled up in problems,

67
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,040
why not pull this newcomer

68
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,440
to our side?

69
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,160
When there's no way left,

70
00:05:51,350 --> 00:05:52,200
why not give it a try?

71
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,440
It makes sense.

72
00:05:56,510 --> 00:05:57,320
Ji Yingying,

73
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,350
I'm not trying to stop you.

74
00:05:59,550 --> 00:06:00,880
I just want to tell you,

75
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:02,830
in such an unknown place,

76
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:04,390
with such a mysterious person,

77
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,200
why don't you call your ally

78
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:07,200
to join you?

79
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,160
Is it that difficult?

80
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:10,110
Who asked me

81
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:11,920
to give you support before?

82
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:16,640
Why are you so angry?

83
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:17,270
I...

84
00:06:20,110 --> 00:06:21,550
Zhao Xiuyuan also said before

85
00:06:21,550 --> 00:06:23,160
that he would always stand by me,

86
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:24,760
but what happened?

87
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:28,000
I've known him since childhood,

88
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,040
and I got this.

89
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,230
I'm not doubting you.

90
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:36,790
I just

91
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:37,880
have gotten used

92
00:06:38,790 --> 00:06:40,350
to not relying on things

93
00:06:40,350 --> 00:06:41,350
I can't control.

94
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,640
I only trust my own hands

95
00:06:43,950 --> 00:06:45,640
to make myself stronger,

96
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,390
doing things faster and faster.

97
00:07:13,060 --> 00:07:16,490
♪The curve of Spring's first thunder♪

98
00:07:17,370 --> 00:07:21,040
♪Quietly shaping a tangled love♪

99
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:24,820
♪Rain drizzles gently down♪

100
00:07:25,130 --> 00:07:29,300
♪When I first met you, it felt like yesterday's wonder♪

101
00:07:30,140 --> 00:07:33,570
♪Mist softly caresses the tranquil lake's surface♪

102
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,160
I'm not him.

103
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,110
I am Yang Jinglan.

104
00:07:38,110 --> 00:07:38,670
♪The little ripples of early summer rise♪

105
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:42,110
I will keep my promise

106
00:07:43,550 --> 00:07:44,920
for the rest of my life.

107
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,230
♪You painted for me, the delicate arch of your brow♪

108
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,230
Sharing glory and shame together,

109
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,600
I'll never leave you.

110
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,700
♪A tapestry of love, woven into my heart♪

111
00:07:51,700 --> 00:07:55,390
♪As dusk falls, with the sound of sea-bloomed flutes♪

112
00:07:55,990 --> 00:07:59,170
♪Watching swallows gracefully settle upon the branches♪

113
00:07:59,170 --> 00:08:03,290
♪We smell the green plums, and life's sweetness it roots♪

114
00:08:04,530 --> 00:08:08,920
♪I send a silk letter to a high flower tower♪

115
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,390
I... I know.

116
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:16,270
Having an ally like you

117
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:17,790
is my good fortune.

118
00:08:17,790 --> 00:08:20,490
♪With the promise of snow, and time that expands♪

119
00:08:21,130 --> 00:08:25,290
♪You and I, together we roam♪

120
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,520
What's wrong?

121
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:55,640
I...

122
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,030
I still have to continue dyeing silk.

123
00:08:57,590 --> 00:08:58,960
You'd better go back now.

124
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,200
Yaoting!

125
00:09:01,670 --> 00:09:02,400
I'm coming!

126
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,550
Yaoting, see Mr. Yang out.

127
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:09,640
Mr. Yang,

128
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,150
this way, please.

129
00:09:12,670 --> 00:09:13,470
Are you really fine?

130
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:35,200
I will keep my promise

131
00:09:36,590 --> 00:09:38,000
for the rest of my life.

132
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:39,640
Sharing glory and shame together,

133
00:09:41,030 --> 00:09:42,000
I'll never leave you.

134
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:30,590
Yaoting!

135
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,640
I've thought of a great idea to add the finishing touch.

136
00:10:34,470 --> 00:10:35,400
What's the idea?

137
00:10:51,670 --> 00:10:52,470
Dear.

138
00:10:55,150 --> 00:10:55,960
Get out.

139
00:10:58,550 --> 00:10:59,280
Dear,

140
00:10:59,910 --> 00:11:01,030
I've personally made

141
00:11:01,030 --> 00:11:02,200
this ginseng soup for you.

142
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:05,280
You've worked hard recently.

143
00:11:07,350 --> 00:11:08,320
Drink the soup

144
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:10,790
and come back to rest with me.

145
00:11:17,590 --> 00:11:18,640
Dear,

146
00:11:19,470 --> 00:11:21,350
we've been married for a while now,

147
00:11:21,710 --> 00:11:23,440
yet you sleep in the study every night,

148
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,640
not even touching me once.

149
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:30,840
All of the Zhao family's members see this clearly.

150
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,840
Do you care what others think of you?

151
00:11:42,550 --> 00:11:44,000
Why did we get married?

152
00:11:44,790 --> 00:11:46,790
The whole Zhao family knows why.

153
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:50,110
Don't think I don't know

154
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,200
what you are planning to do.

155
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,000
I just want a peaceful marriage,

156
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:00,470
but now

157
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,200
it seems like a plot?

158
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:07,080
What kind of person are you,

159
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,960
thinking of a peaceful marriage?

160
00:12:11,790 --> 00:12:14,280
You only want to get pregnant with my child,

161
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,790
and then I'll be useless.

162
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:17,550
Then you can legitimately control

163
00:12:17,550 --> 00:12:19,400
the entire Zhao family.

164
00:12:26,550 --> 00:12:29,200
Dear, are you designing new tribute brocade patterns?

165
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:32,640
Isn't the Zhao family's old ones good enough?

166
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:36,350
Or do you want to learn from Ji Yingying

167
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:37,670
to amaze everyone,

168
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:40,030
to be valued by Chang'an,

169
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:42,000
to be valued by the Military Commissioner?

170
00:12:42,790 --> 00:12:43,710
After that,

171
00:12:43,880 --> 00:12:47,030
you won't need to rely on my Niu family's power anymore, right?

172
00:12:52,550 --> 00:12:54,760
I heard that the other day,

173
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:57,470
you sent a message to Ji Yingying.

174
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:58,790
As for the Yu family,

175
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:01,590
you purposely excluded them

176
00:13:02,230 --> 00:13:04,150
and sent them to Ji Yingying, right?

177
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:07,760
If my father knew

178
00:13:08,470 --> 00:13:11,200
that you are such a double-dealing person,

179
00:13:12,350 --> 00:13:14,150
I don't know what he would think.

180
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:16,000
He probably hasn't had the mood lately

181
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:18,200
to listen to his daughter who's been repeatedly defeated

182
00:13:18,470 --> 00:13:19,590
talking nonsense.

183
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:21,840
Zhao Ping!

184
00:13:24,710 --> 00:13:25,320
Sir.

185
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:26,790
From now on, no one is allowed

186
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:29,000
into my room without my permission.

187
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,000
Otherwise,

188
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,150
beat them to death.

189
00:13:36,550 --> 00:13:37,350
Yes, sir.

190
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,590
What great courage you have.

191
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,350
Without you,

192
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:51,670
my Zhao family would still weave brocade for General Niu.

193
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,280
But without me,

194
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:55,590
you would

195
00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:57,200
be worthless.

196
00:13:57,790 --> 00:13:59,320
As for what's of greater importance,

197
00:14:00,230 --> 00:14:01,400
you know it better than me.

198
00:14:09,540 --> 00:14:11,710
[Yuebuhuan Inn]

199
00:14:11,710 --> 00:14:12,760
Sir, please come in.

200
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:17,790
Mr. Yu, the brocade is about to be made.

201
00:14:17,790 --> 00:14:20,110
Our Bloom Society also has skilled weavers.

202
00:14:20,470 --> 00:14:22,670
Today, I'd like to recommend someone to you.

203
00:14:26,080 --> 00:14:28,960
I'm Ji Yaoting from the Ji family. Greetings.

204
00:14:29,590 --> 00:14:31,110
I'm not good at pattern design

205
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:33,320
but excel in the weaving process.

206
00:14:33,590 --> 00:14:35,590
I'm willing to lend a hand to you.

207
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,320
Mr. Ji, please sit.

208
00:14:37,590 --> 00:14:38,520
Thank you, Mr. Yu.

209
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:43,440
For nine years,

210
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:45,150
my hands

211
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,150
have never rested.

212
00:14:55,350 --> 00:14:57,960
Your skill is no less than before.

213
00:14:58,550 --> 00:15:01,880
Our workshop welcomes you to join us.

214
00:15:03,470 --> 00:15:04,520
Thank you, Mr. Yu.

215
00:15:06,470 --> 00:15:07,280
Mr. Yu,

216
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:09,230
I have another matter to discuss today.

217
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:13,280
The Grain Brocade is ancient,

218
00:15:13,470 --> 00:15:14,520
simple, and rich in tradition,

219
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,840
but people nowadays are seeking something new.

220
00:15:17,350 --> 00:15:18,520
Just relying on the existing patterns

221
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:20,150
might not attract enough attention.

222
00:15:20,350 --> 00:15:23,080
I want to increase its liveliness and shine

223
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:25,280
without changing the original patterns.

224
00:15:25,670 --> 00:15:28,030
Perhaps by adjusting the silk thread colors

225
00:15:28,030 --> 00:15:29,520
or reworking the patterns

226
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:31,320
to make it gleam and shine.

227
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:34,080
Then, we'll get a Rippling Grain Brocade.

228
00:15:34,670 --> 00:15:36,550
Rippling Grain Brocade?

229
00:15:39,710 --> 00:15:41,080
Golden grain ears

230
00:15:42,880 --> 00:15:45,030
sway in the wind,

231
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:48,840
stirring up waves of rice.

232
00:15:53,470 --> 00:15:54,350
Miss Ji,

233
00:15:55,440 --> 00:15:57,550
the light and dark gloss of brocade

234
00:15:57,550 --> 00:15:58,710
generally depends

235
00:15:59,230 --> 00:16:04,080
on the gloss of the silk thread and color ratio,

236
00:16:04,230 --> 00:16:06,840
as well as the weaving method.

237
00:16:07,470 --> 00:16:11,670
To emphasize the sense of flowing waves,

238
00:16:12,110 --> 00:16:14,710
the technique and color ratio

239
00:16:14,710 --> 00:16:16,710
must be innovative.

240
00:16:17,350 --> 00:16:19,640
Of course, the difficulty

241
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:22,910
is no less than developing a new type of brocade.

242
00:16:25,150 --> 00:16:28,470
I haven't even restored

243
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:31,590
the Grain Brocade pattern yet,

244
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:35,110
and you want me to weave it with a rippling effect?

245
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:40,280
That truly is a hard task.

246
00:16:41,150 --> 00:16:43,320
My elder brother also said this yesterday.

247
00:16:44,230 --> 00:16:45,440
But I believe

248
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,760
since we're going to weave it,

249
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:48,880
why not make it the best we can?

250
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:51,150
I can help with the coloring.

251
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:54,150
We can borrow the technique from Shu embroidery for the patterns.

252
00:16:54,470 --> 00:16:55,710
But for the weaving method,

253
00:16:55,710 --> 00:16:57,470
we still need you and the masters

254
00:16:57,470 --> 00:16:58,670
to study it further.

255
00:17:01,670 --> 00:17:05,520
Ji Yingying, this research into Rippling Grain Brocade

256
00:17:06,310 --> 00:17:09,280
is not just a technical issue.

257
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:12,230
So, are there any other problems?

258
00:17:12,430 --> 00:17:14,350
Without money, we can't weave brocade.

259
00:17:15,710 --> 00:17:16,680
Miss Ji,

260
00:17:17,950 --> 00:17:19,680
developing a technique

261
00:17:20,070 --> 00:17:23,110
requires a large investment at the start.

262
00:17:24,230 --> 00:17:26,470
But the Yu family and Bloom Society...

263
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:31,070
Wasn't the money I invested before enough?

264
00:17:34,040 --> 00:17:36,680
Thanks to your support,

265
00:17:36,880 --> 00:17:39,880
we were able to provide for the workers and looms.

266
00:17:40,880 --> 00:17:41,920
But,

267
00:17:42,470 --> 00:17:44,160
to research a new brocade...

268
00:17:44,710 --> 00:17:45,560
How much is needed?

269
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:47,280
At least ninety guan.

270
00:17:51,280 --> 00:17:52,070
Mr. Yu,

271
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:54,920
you and Yaoting just focus on studying how to weave it,

272
00:17:55,280 --> 00:17:56,230
as for the money...

273
00:17:56,230 --> 00:17:57,040
Money?

274
00:17:58,000 --> 00:18:00,110
I have enough money,

275
00:18:00,710 --> 00:18:02,470
and I look handsome.

276
00:18:02,470 --> 00:18:04,470
So why doesn't she like me?

277
00:18:07,760 --> 00:18:09,470
It's Mr. Sang.

278
00:18:12,350 --> 00:18:13,230
Miss Ji,

279
00:18:13,950 --> 00:18:14,950
please continue.

280
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:18,040
As for the money, I'll figure out.

281
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:19,040
Figure it out?

282
00:18:19,950 --> 00:18:23,830
She doesn't like me, but what can I figure it out?

283
00:18:25,070 --> 00:18:27,040
I'm not attached to her!

284
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:29,950
Mr. Yu,

285
00:18:29,950 --> 00:18:31,680
