286
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:32,680
our honorary president properly.

287
00:18:33,470 --> 00:18:34,280
Apologies.

288
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:36,000
I've thought it over.

289
00:18:36,470 --> 00:18:38,590
Even if my father kills me,

290
00:18:38,590 --> 00:18:40,430
I'll still marry into her family!

291
00:18:40,830 --> 00:18:42,280
Shut up!

292
00:18:44,190 --> 00:18:45,880
What does it have to do with you?

293
00:18:45,950 --> 00:18:47,760
I can say that if I like.

294
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,110
I still...

295
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:56,520
You dare to pour on me?

296
00:18:57,040 --> 00:18:59,430
Don't think you can bully me

297
00:18:59,430 --> 00:19:00,710
just because I don't hit women.

298
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:02,560
I'm pouring it on you!

299
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,520
Look at you, howling here.

300
00:19:04,760 --> 00:19:06,040
If this rumor spreads,

301
00:19:06,040 --> 00:19:07,710
how will Pin ever face anyone again?

302
00:19:09,110 --> 00:19:10,880
I didn't think that far.

303
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:12,350
Then what did you think?

304
00:19:14,070 --> 00:19:17,310
I just want to be the kind of man Pin likes

305
00:19:18,040 --> 00:19:20,830
who can share with her the trials and triumphs of life

306
00:19:20,830 --> 00:19:22,590
and will stand beside her in battle.

307
00:19:24,310 --> 00:19:26,110
But I'm not that kind of man.

308
00:19:26,280 --> 00:19:27,520
What should I do, Yingying?

309
00:19:28,310 --> 00:19:30,680
Don't worry about what kind of man Pin likes.

310
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:34,160
Think about what kind of man you want to be first.

311
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:35,470
Me?

312
00:19:45,350 --> 00:19:46,350
To be a man,

313
00:19:47,560 --> 00:19:49,190
a man of integrity,

314
00:19:49,190 --> 00:19:51,470
a man with a purpose, with money to earn,

315
00:19:51,470 --> 00:19:53,760
and a proper man who is respected.

316
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:57,560
What does that mean?

317
00:19:58,070 --> 00:20:00,070
You want me to join you in dyeing silk?

318
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:01,920
I wouldn't know how.

319
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:04,040
Everyone has their own strengths.

320
00:20:04,310 --> 00:20:06,830
I happen to have something that suits you.

321
00:20:07,470 --> 00:20:08,280
What is it?

322
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:10,950
Making money.

323
00:20:18,790 --> 00:20:21,160
[Rongjin Silk]

324
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:22,110
Mr. Wang!

325
00:20:22,470 --> 00:20:23,280
Here!

326
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:25,310
Hello, Mr. Wang.

327
00:20:26,920 --> 00:20:28,950
Our Bloom Society has partnered with the Yu family

328
00:20:28,950 --> 00:20:30,110
to create the Rippling Grain Brocade.

329
00:20:30,430 --> 00:20:32,560
We warmly invite you to invest.

330
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:33,430
We hope for your support.

331
00:20:33,430 --> 00:20:34,470
[Invitation]
In three days,

332
00:20:34,470 --> 00:20:36,350
we will have an auction at the Yuebuhuan Inn.

333
00:20:36,470 --> 00:20:38,470
We would be honored if you could attend!

334
00:20:38,520 --> 00:20:41,310
Okay, I will definitely go to the Bloom Society's event.

335
00:20:41,310 --> 00:20:42,230
I will surely attend.

336
00:20:42,310 --> 00:20:43,280
I will definitely support you!

337
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:46,920
Rippling Grain Brocade.

338
00:20:47,470 --> 00:20:48,680
We warmly invite you to invest in it.

339
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:49,920
Profits will be shared.

340
00:20:51,350 --> 00:20:54,110
She wants us to invest before the brocade is completed?

341
00:20:54,280 --> 00:20:55,430
I told you

342
00:20:55,430 --> 00:20:57,070
that she would surely surprise me.

343
00:20:57,760 --> 00:20:59,070
As long as we start from scratch

344
00:20:59,070 --> 00:21:00,070
and begin again with her,

345
00:21:00,470 --> 00:21:02,430
we'll learn how to weave it.

346
00:21:04,280 --> 00:21:06,280
She and Mr. Yang are quite close,

347
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:07,280
getting along well.

348
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:09,350
Mr. Yang is also investigating...

349
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:11,800
Sheng,

350
00:21:11,950 --> 00:21:14,230
you should stay away from Ji Yingying

351
00:21:14,350 --> 00:21:15,520
and avoid getting into trouble.

352
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:16,680
They're in love,

353
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:17,760
but I'm not interested.

354
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:20,040
The one who loses won't be me.

355
00:21:21,110 --> 00:21:22,280
But these women,

356
00:21:22,560 --> 00:21:23,880
once they fall in love,

357
00:21:24,230 --> 00:21:27,040
it often clouds their judgment and choices.

358
00:21:28,070 --> 00:21:30,350
If Ji Yingying wants to develop her career,

359
00:21:30,350 --> 00:21:31,560
that's not good for her.

360
00:21:32,070 --> 00:21:33,520
I need to come up with a plan

361
00:21:33,760 --> 00:21:35,880
to keep her away from Yang Jinglan.

362
00:21:38,950 --> 00:21:41,280
Miss Ji really came up with a good idea.

363
00:21:41,760 --> 00:21:43,470
But these people are afraid of offending Niu Jin

364
00:21:43,470 --> 00:21:45,160
and don't dare to buy silk from Bloom Society, right?

365
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:45,710
Do they dare to buy

366
00:21:46,070 --> 00:21:46,950
this brocade?

367
00:21:47,350 --> 00:21:48,350
Behind every wealthy brocade merchant,

368
00:21:48,350 --> 00:21:49,680
no one is without support.

369
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:51,640
Offending Niu Jin because of a few baskets of silk?

370
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:52,470
That's definitely not worth it.

371
00:21:52,760 --> 00:21:54,040
But this brocade is different.

372
00:21:54,310 --> 00:21:56,110
With great profits comes great risk.

373
00:21:56,470 --> 00:21:57,310
Even if they don't buy it,

374
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:58,560
they must still take a look.

375
00:22:01,430 --> 00:22:02,880
I know, I'm quite carefree,

376
00:22:03,070 --> 00:22:05,230
but you don't have to look at me like that.

377
00:22:07,110 --> 00:22:08,230
Well,

378
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:09,710
you appear reckless and carefree,

379
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:10,680
but actually,

380
00:22:11,310 --> 00:22:12,760
you're quite practical and shrewd.

381
00:22:15,280 --> 00:22:16,280
You ungrateful child!

382
00:22:16,280 --> 00:22:16,950
Let's go!

383
00:22:17,230 --> 00:22:18,110
Just watch the fun.

384
00:22:19,160 --> 00:22:19,950
You brute!

385
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:30,160
Here... Let's hide!

386
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:31,160
What's going on?

387
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:31,950
What's happening?

388
00:22:35,280 --> 00:22:38,520
Isn't that the famous Mr. Yang?

389
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:40,310
Welcome!

390
00:22:42,310 --> 00:22:44,230
Please, come inside.

391
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:51,430
Shisi,

392
00:22:52,110 --> 00:22:53,560
others would entertain you before,

393
00:22:53,560 --> 00:22:55,680
but now you're the one hosting others.

394
00:22:57,710 --> 00:22:59,070
Your father's been dismissed?

395
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:01,230
Can you stop bringing up my father?

396
00:23:01,470 --> 00:23:03,070
He gets a headache just hearing about you.

397
00:23:03,760 --> 00:23:05,710
I'm the honorary president of the Bloom Society now.

398
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:07,710
If anything happens, I'll definitely help.

399
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:08,710
Besides,

400
00:23:08,710 --> 00:23:09,760
with my abilities,

401
00:23:09,760 --> 00:23:11,760
I can easily host guests.

402
00:23:16,470 --> 00:23:17,470
I just remembered.

403
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:19,070
Yingying said

404
00:23:19,070 --> 00:23:20,070
you're the Brocade Officer,

405
00:23:21,040 --> 00:23:22,040
you can't place a bid,

406
00:23:22,280 --> 00:23:23,950
so she didn't leave you a private room.

407
00:23:25,470 --> 00:23:26,830
So you mean

408
00:23:27,040 --> 00:23:28,070
we should leave?

409
00:23:29,280 --> 00:23:30,830
Mr. Bai, this way, please.

410
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:35,920
Does he have a private room?

411
00:23:36,880 --> 00:23:37,680
He...

412
00:23:38,830 --> 00:23:39,640
he does.

413
00:23:46,430 --> 00:23:47,950
It seems Miss Ji doesn't welcome me.

414
00:23:48,760 --> 00:23:49,950
Miss Ji, you're welcoming me personally.

415
00:23:49,950 --> 00:23:51,710
I'm truly flattered.

416
00:23:53,310 --> 00:23:54,880
You're wealthy. It suits you.

417
00:23:57,400 --> 00:23:57,950
Mr. Yang.

418
00:23:59,430 --> 00:24:00,280
This way, please.

419
00:24:03,110 --> 00:24:03,920
I'll need a private room.

420
00:24:08,470 --> 00:24:10,830
Mr. Yang, Mr. Zhuge, please have a seat.

421
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:12,310
This is the spot reserved for our people.

422
00:24:13,560 --> 00:24:14,470
Say it again.

423
00:24:15,160 --> 00:24:16,760
Are you going to sit or not?

424
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:18,520
I'll sit.

425
00:24:19,710 --> 00:24:20,560
I'm one of your people.

426
00:24:22,280 --> 00:24:22,590
Mr. Bai,

427
00:24:22,590 --> 00:24:22,920
Let's sit.

428
00:24:22,920 --> 00:24:23,310
This way.

429
00:24:23,520 --> 00:24:24,000
- Sit. - After you.

430
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:26,190
I'm one of her people.

431
00:24:44,950 --> 00:24:45,710
Feel yourself at home.

432
00:24:52,950 --> 00:24:53,760
Mr. Yu.

433
00:24:55,110 --> 00:24:56,110
You...

434
00:24:56,280 --> 00:24:57,520
Mrs. Yang...

435
00:24:57,520 --> 00:24:58,470
What's the matter?

436
00:24:59,520 --> 00:25:00,310
I run this inn.

437
00:25:00,310 --> 00:25:01,350
She's here for the feast.

438
00:25:01,350 --> 00:25:02,310
Everyone's here to make money.

439
00:25:02,310 --> 00:25:03,280
Is there something wrong with that?

440
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:04,470
I...

441
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:11,760
Have a seat.

442
00:25:15,350 --> 00:25:16,310
Did you learn something new?

443
00:25:16,470 --> 00:25:19,280
Women in Shu have different temperaments.

444
00:25:19,520 --> 00:25:21,040
If you upset them,

445
00:25:21,280 --> 00:25:22,950
it's hard to calm them down.

446
00:25:27,350 --> 00:25:28,190
Miss Ji,

447
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,040
may your business thrive.

448
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:42,310
All colleagues from Yizhou,

449
00:25:42,560 --> 00:25:43,680
greetings to all.

450
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:46,880
As you all know,

451
00:25:46,950 --> 00:25:49,110
Our Bloom Society and the Yu family

452
00:25:49,470 --> 00:25:51,640
will jointly research and weave a new brocade.

453
00:25:52,070 --> 00:25:53,160
As we all know,

454
00:25:53,350 --> 00:25:54,560
the new brocade

455
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:56,110
will certainly sell well.

456
00:25:57,920 --> 00:26:00,040
Today, I invite all shopkeepers here.

457
00:26:00,560 --> 00:26:02,640
What we are bidding on is not the new brocade itself

458
00:26:03,280 --> 00:26:06,070
but the high profits

459
00:26:06,470 --> 00:26:07,760
it represents.

460
00:26:08,280 --> 00:26:08,880
The winning bidder

461
00:26:08,880 --> 00:26:11,430
will receive a 20% share of the profits from this new brocade.

462
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:12,920
In other words,

463
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:15,950
if every roll of brocade sells for ten guan,

464
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:19,110
the winning bidder will receive two guan as their share.

465
00:26:23,470 --> 00:26:24,470
The new brocade is still not finished,

466
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:26,430
so today I will show you

467
00:26:26,430 --> 00:26:28,280
the design of this brocade.

468
00:26:28,710 --> 00:26:29,830
Please take a look.

469
00:26:38,350 --> 00:26:39,470
Outside Yizhou City,

470
00:26:39,470 --> 00:26:41,640
there is a place called Gubei Village.

471
00:26:41,800 --> 00:26:43,640
It has worshiped the God of Grain for generations.

472
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:46,880
The wheat pattern brocade is the village's belief.

473
00:26:48,280 --> 00:26:51,310
The wheat is a gift from the God of Grain,

474
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:54,160
giving people food to fill their stomachs.

475
00:26:54,950 --> 00:26:57,430
The silk is a blessing from Leizu,

476
00:26:57,680 --> 00:26:59,880
giving people clothes to keep warm.

477
00:27:00,640 --> 00:27:02,470
The flowing waves on this brocade

478
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:04,760
are light, water,

479
00:27:05,110 --> 00:27:05,830
and wind,

480
00:27:06,280 --> 00:27:09,310
the gifts bestowed upon us by heaven.

481
00:27:17,950 --> 00:27:19,160
The starting bid is 20 guan.

482
00:27:19,560 --> 00:27:21,040
The auction begins.

483
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:47,560
Why isn't anyone bidding?

484
00:27:48,590 --> 00:27:50,950
They're probably worried it can't be made.

485
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:52,310
Mr. Zhuge,

486
00:27:52,680 --> 00:27:55,160
our Bloom Society will never deceive others.

487
00:27:55,470 --> 00:27:56,230
I...

488
00:27:57,280 --> 00:27:58,520
I didn't mean it that way.

489
00:27:58,590 --> 00:28:00,760
To these people, the money

490
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:01,950
is just a drop in the bucket.

491
00:28:02,110 --> 00:28:03,110
They don't doubt us,

492
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:04,800
but no one wants

493
00:28:04,800 --> 00:28:06,310
to be the first to speak up.

494
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:09,350
You won't want to bid, will you?

495
00:28:10,310 --> 00:28:11,710
If the Brocade Officer places a bid,

496
00:28:12,280 --> 00:28:13,520
who would dare to bid after that?

497
00:28:15,070 --> 00:28:15,950
I don't have money.

498
00:28:16,710 --> 00:28:17,560
I'm just supporting the event.

499
00:28:26,070 --> 00:28:27,190
This brocade

500
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:29,110
has both ancient heritage

501
00:28:29,110 --> 00:28:30,000
and fresh innovation.

502
00:28:30,280 --> 00:28:31,350
I really like it.

503
00:28:33,190 --> 00:28:35,710
How about I take care of it

504
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:37,280
and help you invite

505
00:28:37,280 --> 00:28:40,350
the Military Commissioner to generously open his purse?

506
00:28:41,710 --> 00:28:42,520
Mr. Yang,

507
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:46,310
why bother the Military Commissioner with such a small matter?

508
00:28:46,470 --> 00:28:48,070
Once the brocade is made,

509
00:28:48,070 --> 00:28:50,520
it won't be too late to present it to him.

510
00:28:52,920 --> 00:28:53,710
If none of you

511
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:56,710
place a bid,

512
00:28:57,590 --> 00:28:58,280
when

513
00:28:58,880 --> 00:29:00,160
will this brocade be completed?

514
00:29:02,350 --> 00:29:03,760
How about this, Miss Ji?

515
00:29:05,310 --> 00:29:06,920
If the first person to bid

516
00:29:07,110 --> 00:29:08,950
wins the auction for this brocade,

517
00:29:09,590 --> 00:29:10,880
what benefit will they get?

518
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:14,310
They'll get one guan off the price.

519
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:16,110
If it doesn't sell,

520
00:29:16,590 --> 00:29:18,280
the first bidder will get

521
00:29:18,280 --> 00:29:20,710
a 10% discount on their first silk order

522
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:23,920
from Bloom Society in the future.

523
00:29:24,430 --> 00:29:26,110
Even if it doesn't sell, there's still a benefit?

524
00:29:26,590 --> 00:29:27,560
Then I bid...

525
00:29:27,560 --> 00:29:28,520
Twenty-one guan!

526
00:29:47,950 --> 00:29:49,000
I bid twenty-one guan.

527
00:29:49,680 --> 00:29:51,800
Is anyone going to raise the price?

528
00:30:02,800 --> 00:30:03,590
Sir,

529
00:30:04,710 --> 00:30:06,920
if the Zhao family wins the bid,

530
00:30:08,070 --> 00:30:10,070
this brocade may never be seen again.

531
00:30:11,310 --> 00:30:12,310
Let's wait a little longer.

532
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:15,070
Miss Ji,

533
00:30:15,560 --> 00:30:16,880
the highest bidder wins.

534
00:30:17,350 --> 00:30:18,520
The hammer is about to fall.

535
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:22,520
I bid sixty guan!

536
00:30:30,950 --> 00:30:31,830
Miss Ji,

537
00:30:32,470 --> 00:30:33,590
my wife doesn't understand brocade

538
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:35,520
and doesn't know the value of this new brocade.

539
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:36,760
I'm willing to bid sixty guan.

540
00:30:44,680 --> 00:30:46,160
You're discrediting your own wife

541
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:47,880
and raising the price for another woman.

542
00:30:48,310 --> 00:30:51,110
My Dear really does things in such a unique way.

543
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:52,880
I can't compare to you.

544
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:57,520
Mr. Zhao, Mrs. Zhao,

545
00:30:58,110 --> 00:30:59,110
I remember

546
00:30:59,110 --> 00:31:00,800
I didn't invite you two.

547
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:02,710
Why are you here?

548
00:31:04,430 --> 00:31:05,920
Because we've heard a lot about it.

549
00:31:06,470 --> 00:31:07,070
What?

550
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:09,280
My husband bid on this brocade.

551
00:31:09,710 --> 00:31:12,110
Do you intend to deny it?

552
00:31:13,950 --> 00:31:15,280
You weren't here earlier,

553
00:31:15,310 --> 00:31:16,800
so you didn't hear my introduction.

554
00:31:17,470 --> 00:31:20,230
This brocade carries the belief of an ancient village.

555
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:23,110
The village has worshipped the God of Grain for generations.

556
00:31:23,950 --> 00:31:25,280
Before the auction,

557
00:31:25,310 --> 00:31:27,760
the village chief even had a divination done.

558
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:28,760
It's forbidden

559
00:31:28,760 --> 00:31:30,110
for anyone who has dealt with military affairs.

560
00:31:31,110 --> 00:31:32,520
That's why I didn't invite you two.

561
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:35,110
You can't bid, I'm afraid.

562
00:31:37,280 --> 00:31:39,430
Since when do the customs of a wild village

563
00:31:39,430 --> 00:31:41,710
require the Brocade Master to follow?

564
00:31:43,400 --> 00:31:44,800
Do you all still remember

565
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:46,350
who is the leader

566
00:31:46,640 --> 00:31:48,640
