567
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:59,520
I've already reported this matter to the Brocade Bureau.

568
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:05,710
I think I'm worth the Brocade Master and his wife

569
00:32:06,350 --> 00:32:07,950
to observe this rule.

570
00:32:09,950 --> 00:32:11,400
It's really hard to go against heaven's will

571
00:32:11,400 --> 00:32:12,520
and the law of the land.

572
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:15,070
I cannot give this brocade to you two.

573
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:18,830
Fine,

574
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:20,880
then I will see for myself

575
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:22,190
who heaven and the law will favor,

576
00:32:22,310 --> 00:32:25,470
and whose hands this brocade will fall into.

577
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:33,040
Fine,

578
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:36,520
then I'll let you have a good look.

579
00:32:37,830 --> 00:32:38,710
Please, lift the curtain.

580
00:32:42,680 --> 00:32:43,710
[From Zuo Zhuan, Year 10 of Duke Huan]
"A common man is innocent,

581
00:32:43,710 --> 00:32:44,800
but holding jade is a crime."

582
00:32:45,190 --> 00:32:46,710
I had also anticipated

583
00:32:46,710 --> 00:32:48,470
that you might not want to make a big scene,

584
00:32:48,710 --> 00:32:50,880
so I made early preparations.

585
00:32:51,110 --> 00:32:53,110
[Sign "Heaven No. 2"]
Each room has its own number,

586
00:32:53,110 --> 00:32:54,160
a silk thread,

587
00:32:54,830 --> 00:32:56,280
corresponding to a bell on stage.

588
00:32:57,430 --> 00:32:58,710
Who does the bell belong to?

589
00:32:58,710 --> 00:33:01,110
Only you and the Bloom Society know.

590
00:33:01,470 --> 00:33:02,520
It will not be leaked.

591
00:33:03,590 --> 00:33:04,920
If anyone wants to bid,

592
00:33:05,110 --> 00:33:06,590
pull the thread in your hand.

593
00:33:06,830 --> 00:33:07,880
When the bell rings,

594
00:33:08,070 --> 00:33:10,110
it means a five-guan increase.

595
00:33:15,920 --> 00:33:18,880
Everyone, let the auction continue!

596
00:33:41,930 --> 00:33:44,150
[Sign "Earth No. 1"]

597
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:57,760
Earth No. 1 bids twenty-five guan.

598
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:05,400
Yellow No. 2 bids

599
00:34:05,560 --> 00:34:06,520
thirty guan.

600
00:34:11,950 --> 00:34:14,320
Heaven No. 1 bids thirty-five guan.

601
00:34:23,080 --> 00:34:24,390
Earth No. 1 bids

602
00:34:24,520 --> 00:34:25,520
fifty guan!

603
00:34:34,150 --> 00:34:36,120
Fifty guan is not a small amount.

604
00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:38,080
