608
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:57,520
We, the Yang family, are willing to bid seventy guan.

609
00:34:57,670 --> 00:34:58,760
Seventy!

610
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:02,080
Seventy guan!

611
00:35:06,120 --> 00:35:07,320
Isn't this supposed to be blind bidding?

612
00:35:07,600 --> 00:35:09,320
What does the Yang family mean by this?

613
00:35:10,470 --> 00:35:12,600
Mrs. Yang is truly brave.

614
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:21,560
Crooked merchant.

615
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:25,280
