616
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,560
It seems you're not worried

617
00:35:26,560 --> 00:35:27,910
about me at all.

618
00:35:28,560 --> 00:35:29,600
When it comes to doing business,

619
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:31,390
you're more talented.

620
00:35:32,080 --> 00:35:34,320
I'm looking forward to your next move.

621
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,600
Earth No. 1 bids

622
00:35:51,600 --> 00:35:52,600
eighty guan!

623
00:35:53,040 --> 00:35:56,120
This Earth No. 1 seems determined to win.

624
00:36:03,120 --> 00:36:03,710
Go ahead.

625
00:36:09,600 --> 00:36:10,560
I am willing

626
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:12,280
to bid ninety guan.

627
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:24,950
We, the Yang family, bid ninety-five guan.

628
00:36:28,150 --> 00:36:29,470
I offer one hundred guan.

629
00:36:46,390 --> 00:36:47,560
One hundred guan, once.

630
00:36:52,190 --> 00:36:54,560
[Sign "Earth No. 1"]
One hundred guan is more than enough!

631
00:36:54,910 --> 00:36:56,670
So can we withdraw

632
00:36:56,870 --> 00:36:58,560
after completing our task?

633
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:09,280
One hundred guan, once.

634
00:37:17,600 --> 00:37:19,190
Earth No. 1 bids

635
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:21,520
one hundred five guan.

636
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,800
Thanks to my great idea.

637
00:37:33,800 --> 00:37:35,560
But you both

638
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:37,760
don't understand people's hearts.

639
00:37:42,910 --> 00:37:45,320
Earth No. 1 bid one hundred five guan.

640
00:37:46,150 --> 00:37:48,040
Is there anyone else willing to raise the bid?

641
00:38:01,190 --> 00:38:02,760
One hundred five guan, once.

642
00:38:10,710 --> 00:38:12,710
One hundred five guan, twice.

643
00:38:13,630 --> 00:38:14,470
Twice already!

644
00:38:17,710 --> 00:38:18,950
This should not be happening.

645
00:38:19,870 --> 00:38:21,520
I've dominated the gambling scene for so many years,

646
00:38:21,670 --> 00:38:23,760
and I can clearly see that Bai Sheng will win this.

647
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:24,950
If this fails,

648
00:38:24,950 --> 00:38:26,760
Yingying will kill us...

649
00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:28,080
she will kill you!

650
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:33,320
Mr. Bai,

651
00:38:34,870 --> 00:38:35,910
do you want to raise the bid?

652
00:38:43,910 --> 00:38:45,080
I think

653
00:38:46,520 --> 00:38:48,910
it's better not to steal from others.

654
00:38:55,120 --> 00:38:55,950
Miss Ji,

655
00:38:56,630 --> 00:38:57,520
please go ahead.

656
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:08,520
Earth No. 1, one hundred five guan, three times.

657
00:39:10,760 --> 00:39:11,560
Sold.

658
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:25,910
It's Sang Shisi, right?

659
00:39:26,760 --> 00:39:28,080
Unworthy guy.

660
00:40:04,190 --> 00:40:05,910
Miss Ji, you don't need to be so polite.

661
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:08,120
I just placed two bids

662
00:40:08,120 --> 00:40:09,470
to support you.

663
00:40:14,120 --> 00:40:15,120
"Earth No. 1" is us.

664
00:40:19,320 --> 00:40:20,670
I really didn't expect this.

665
00:40:20,670 --> 00:40:22,040
Miss Ji,

666
00:40:22,430 --> 00:40:23,520
you're so honest.

667
00:40:30,470 --> 00:40:31,910
You have already seen through it.

668
00:40:32,280 --> 00:40:33,520
Why should I hide it?

669
00:40:35,520 --> 00:40:37,000
This Rippling Grain Brocade

670
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:39,560
has some connection with you.

671
00:40:39,950 --> 00:40:42,120
Are you willing to invest?

672
00:40:43,710 --> 00:40:45,230
I feel that

673
00:40:45,230 --> 00:40:47,320
the Yang family's bid is quite generous.

674
00:40:47,520 --> 00:40:50,190
Why do you choose me?

675
00:40:50,950 --> 00:40:52,710
The Yang family has too many rules.

676
00:40:52,870 --> 00:40:53,910
The pattern isn't even finished yet.

677
00:40:53,950 --> 00:40:55,910
The process is so difficult.

678
00:40:57,080 --> 00:40:58,710
If I'm not wrong,

679
00:40:59,190 --> 00:41:01,040
the Yang family rejected you

680
00:41:01,040 --> 00:41:01,910
because they thought

681
00:41:02,280 --> 00:41:03,870
if they didn't win the bid publicly

682
00:41:03,870 --> 00:41:05,910
but still got the brocade,

683
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:08,080
they would carry the reputation

684
00:41:08,080 --> 00:41:11,520
of secretly stealing the anonymous buyer's goods.

685
00:41:11,520 --> 00:41:13,910
That reputation doesn't sound good.

686
00:41:14,150 --> 00:41:14,950
However,

687
00:41:15,950 --> 00:41:18,710
my reputation in your eyes

688
00:41:18,950 --> 00:41:20,280
is also insignificant.

689
00:41:21,150 --> 00:41:22,470
Not at all, Mr. Bai.

690
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:25,520
I'm just curious

691
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:28,950
why are you so certain

692
00:41:29,150 --> 00:41:30,600
that I'll agree to your terms?

693
00:41:31,710 --> 00:41:33,470
You always know clearly

694
00:41:33,470 --> 00:41:34,710
what you want.

695
00:41:35,520 --> 00:41:37,320
Since you already anticipated what I would say,

696
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:38,470
why bother coming here

697
00:41:39,080 --> 00:41:40,190
if you're not interested?

698
00:41:42,470 --> 00:41:43,280
Fine.

699
00:41:43,910 --> 00:41:44,710
I can give the money,

700
00:41:44,710 --> 00:41:46,870
but I have my own rules.

701
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:48,280
Please, Mr. Bai.

702
00:41:48,360 --> 00:41:49,000
First,

703
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:51,000
