704
00:41:51,670 --> 00:41:52,150
Fine.

705
00:41:52,190 --> 00:41:52,670
Second,

706
00:41:52,910 --> 00:41:54,120
how the brocade pattern is designed

707
00:41:54,120 --> 00:41:55,080
and how it is woven...

708
00:41:55,080 --> 00:41:56,120
I must know everything.

709
00:41:56,120 --> 00:41:56,710
Third,

710
00:41:57,080 --> 00:41:59,390
I need to oversee the work at the Yu family brocade workshop.

711
00:42:02,390 --> 00:42:03,150
The Yu family brocade workshop

712
00:42:03,150 --> 00:42:04,080
is not like the Ji family

713
00:42:04,080 --> 00:42:05,280
or the Bloom Society.

714
00:42:05,430 --> 00:42:06,600
I can't make decisions alone.

715
00:42:06,870 --> 00:42:08,870
This must be decided with Mr. Yu.

716
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:09,800
I agree.

717
00:42:14,600 --> 00:42:15,390
Greetings, Mr. Yu.

718
00:42:16,040 --> 00:42:16,840
Greetings, Mr. Yu.

719
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:22,840
I need you to invest one hundred guan,

720
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:27,190
Not less than that.

721
00:42:28,190 --> 00:42:28,870
As for the weaving,

722
00:42:29,360 --> 00:42:30,360
