723
00:42:30,800 --> 00:42:31,870
No interference is allowed.

724
00:42:32,670 --> 00:42:34,190
I'll follow your arrangements.

725
00:42:34,390 --> 00:42:35,150
Then,

726
00:42:35,560 --> 00:42:36,560
I wish you two

727
00:42:36,950 --> 00:42:38,000
smooth progress in your work.

